thread.title: Notre Dame Wins Women’s College Basketball Title

author: Jim Chairusmi
title: Notre Dame Wins Women’s College Basketball Title

organizations.name: notre dame wins women’s college basketball title notre dame

text:
Notre Dame women’s basketball coach Muffet McGraw called it her toughest season, with only seven healthy scholarship players available for the Final Four.
“We just constantly focus on what we have, what we can do, who’s going to step up?” McGraw said ahead of Sunday’s championship game against Mississippi State.
